        <h2>About the Agency</h2>
        <p>Operation Shadow is an advanced intelligence-gathering system designed to empower agents with secure access to the dark web for legitimate purposes, such as cybersecurity, risk assessment, and critical research. Our AI is engineered to maximize confidentiality and data integrity while minimizing exposure to dangerous elements.</p>
