    <section id="faq">
        <h2>Intel FAQ</h2>
        <p><strong>What is the dark web?</strong> The dark web is a hidden layer of the internet used for a variety of activities, both legal and illegal. Our tool focuses on ethical and secure navigation for intelligence purposes.</p>
        <p><strong>Is this mission legal?</strong> Absolutely. Operation Shadow is designed to ensure compliance with all legal standards. We support only legal and ethical operations, such as cybersecurity research, investigative journalism, and privacy protection.</p>
        <p><strong>How does the agent ensure my anonymity?</strong> Our agent integrates with industry-standard encryption and anonymity tools, such as Tor and VPNs, to keep your identity and mission secure at all costs.</p>
        <p><strong>Can I conduct illegal activities using this system?</strong> Negative. Operation Shadow is strictly for lawful intelligence purposes. Any attempt to use the agent for illicit activities will be flagged and blocked.</p>
